data.title: Henry Hughes
data.text:
Biography

Henry (Harry) Hughes was born on July 18th 1909, the fifth of 8 children of Michael Hughes & Annie Green.

He is listed in the 1911 census at age 2, living with his parents.

Harry was married to Kitty oâ€™Rourke and they had 14 children, (some of the names were, Gerry, Michael, Vincent, Martin, Brendan, Aine, Joan, Rosealeen, & Eamon) they lived in Seatown Villas, Swords, Co Dublin. Harry worked as a security guard for a number of years in Technicon (now Bayer) in Swords.
